# vim-pandoc-syntax

standalone pandoc syntax module.

forked from the version provided by `fmoralesc/vim-pantondoc`

compatible with vim versions having `+conceal`.

## features

* pretty display using `conceal`.
* region based syntax matching, fixes problems with spans in the version in
  `vim-pandoc` and `vim-pandondoc`.
* includes tests, to ease development.

